; Ready-to-fly quadcopter — one GWMulticopter node that self-assembles its SITL
; bridge, model, and (optional) camera. Instance into a scene with a camera, run
; SITL with VEHICLE=ArduCopter, and connect. Tick `enable_camera` for video; swap
; `config` / `model_scene` for your own.
